data.description: You will love this updated, gorgeous 3bed, 2 bath home located in a beautiful Chandler neighborhood! Many wonderful features throughout such as NO HOA, upgraded energy-efficient windows, upgraded landscaping sprinkler systems (SEE DOCUMENTS), cozy fireplace, and refreshing private diving pool. This property has an easy entrance RV gate, covered patio in back and front, and 2 sheds for extra storage space! You'll love the flow of the kitchen space into the dining area, as well as the formal living room with seating area. The main bedroom features access to the backyard and a full bath. Come see this AMAZING home before it is too late!
